  "prompt": "How much should I expect to pay for a 1-car caltrain wrap advertisement?",
  "response": "The cost of a 1-car Caltrain wrap advertisement can vary significantly based on several factors, including the duration of the campaign, the design complexity, and the specific terms negotiated with the advertising company. As of the most recent data, prices for transit advertising can range from tens of thousands to hundreds of thousands of dollars per month.\n\nFor a more accurate estimate, it would be best to contact Caltrain directly or consult with an advertising agency that specializes in transit ads. They can provide you with detailed pricing based on your specific needs and the current market rates.",
